title: Support Plz
body:
Hi. 
Just wanting some support with a youtube channel i have just made. My name is Migaloo HD and I do anything league of legends and some minecraft too. I hope you enjoy the videos, hit subscribe, like the videos, comment advice, just pretty much anything. The url: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuLrukkclX4oRCcGTA5t2Ag 
If that doesn't work just search up Migaloo HD on youtube. I'm sure you'll find it. Let your friends know about me. I very much appreciate all the support. I will upload a few videos every week if all goes to plan. Any questions feels free to ask me. Plz subscribe i need all the help i can get to get out there. You wont be disappointed, i promise. Check out my facebook page too https://www.facebook.com/pages/Migaloo-HD/848593838531341?skip_nax_wizard=true&ref_type=bookmark

Migaloo HD  :D

replies.body: oh and btw, there are no league vids out yet but there will definitely be by this weekend. :) If you want to suggest any champs to play in my video or even if you want to play with me just hit that subscribe button and chuck us a message
